Great Britain's Mia Brookes is expected to be taking on reigning champion Anna Gasser in the women's big air snowboarding final at Livigno Snow Park. There is also British interest in the rhythm dance discipline of the ice dance at Milano Ice Skating Arena, with Lilah Fear and Lewis Gibson beginning their campaign to win Team GB's first figure skating medal since Jayne Torvill and Christopher Dean earned bronze in Lillehammer in 1994. There is also semi-final action from curling's mixed doubles tournament at Cortina Curling Olympic Stadium
